{"tid":1739988,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（探討）政府成立「權力監察公署」新部門指日可待","createTime":"2019-11-19T20:48:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T12:49:47.000Z","uid":236080,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1dec0a9190dc654ce8796c9e09552375964569fc","tid":1739988,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T20:48:22.000Z","msg":"中文名稱：權力監察公署<br />\n<br />\n英文名稱：Independent Commission Against  Abuse of Authority（ICAAA)<br />\n<br />\n成立背景：就2019年香港民眾運動中，警察及政府權力過大，不斷地利用自身權力對市民及基層公務員進行打壓，故此事後成立「權力監察公署」(ICAAA) 作長久監察及調查之用。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n部門詳情<br />\n<br />\n政府架構：屬紀律部隊及執法部隊<br />\n<br />\n起薪點：高警隊10% （以突顯階級差異，因重點打擊對象為警隊，與ICAC成立初期相似）<br />\n<br />\n最低投考資格：學士學位/同等學歷 （本地及海外大學適用）<br />\n<br />\n初期招募人手：約500人<br />\n<br />\n聘用方式：合約制 （ICAC相似）<br />\n<br />\n工作範疇：初期以打擊警隊及政府官員首長等濫權為首要任務，並會特設人手去調查及重整721 831等五個多月的抗爭運動，當中各高官及警隊濫用職權的情況。<br />\n<br />\n工作成效：由於是政府下的一個獨立調查部門，所有濫權案件可直接交到法庭審理。相比獨立調查委員會更有效。<br />\n<br />\n入職訓練：槍械及格鬥訓練，另設一套有關權力使用及與濫權有關課程 （約14星期，ICAC相似但貪污轉成濫權）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jLSqghC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjLSqghC.jpg&h=2bb8354e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed9bf925dd87e3749418b7d1b94a075e9c80f7cb","tid":1739988,"uid":236080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T20:49:48.000Z","msg":"一切似空談<br />\n當年香港人都冇諗過ICAC嘅出現"},{"pid":"149c4bf904102faf36a9f3ee791b550b85c8fdb1","tid":1739988,"uid":223525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T20:50:17.000Z","msg":"成立啲咩無意思<br />\n無權力都係收皮<br />\n大至法院都可以俾支那屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70cffd77befaf5fb460ce2f74d75176eee87487a","tid":1739988,"uid":258571,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T20:52:56.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\nUnder警察=監警會<br />\n英國佬做改革就係真係挽救社會<br />\n中國佬做改革只係清末維新<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c7349f3513130d050e7ca5ac9b3a23c1d68f57","tid":1739988,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"149c4bf904102faf36a9f3ee791b550b85c8fdb1","tid":1739988,"uid":223525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T20:50:17.000Z","msg":"成立啲咩無意思<br />\n無權力都係收皮<br />\n大至法院都可以俾支那屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T20:53:43.000Z","msg":"希望起到個阻嚇性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似ICAC咁紙老虎<br />\n都起碼有阻嚇性作用，等啲人怕麻煩都好"},{"pid":"a7bba64a235907ff83b290c6af6637aaae1fbfeb","tid":1739988,"uid":215784,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T20:55:40.000Z","msg":"以為政府搞<br />\n<br />\n原來係你諗出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a52627c6c9bddea03902e8a3c96900a5fce67a","tid":1739988,"uid":93277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T20:56:34.000Z","msg":"你需要一個醫生"},{"pid":"08c794077c89b92e14d75c4a5bd88e0c78d0e34e","tid":1739988,"uid":79974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T20:56:39.000Z","msg":"最撚緊要嘅係，市民，而唔係特首/其他政府部門，可以決定呢個公署有冇糧出，職員犯法/包庇幾時停職，出糧應該每3個月計一次，你班友仔一唔做野就等如有3個月白做，再罰你老母錢/停職<br />\n<br />\n一定要將個權力交由我地去決定，咁班仆街仔先會聽話"},{"pid":"e43b7b36524afc63006c5dee840ce44c97ca211b","tid":1739988,"uid":1493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T20:57:26.000Z","msg":"仲信政府？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d10ac6c22a26dc6b1e7f843780bf8c4e9bf87a","tid":1739988,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70cffd77befaf5fb460ce2f74d75176eee87487a","